OL,3,CWhat to know as countdown begins for
OL,4,Cfirst human Moon mission in 53 years
OL,6,FIt's been over 50 years since a human
OL,7,Fflew to the Moon.
OL,9,FNow, with the help of a rocket taller
OL,10,Fthan Big Ben and the first spacecraft
OL,11,Fof its kind to house humans, NASA is
OL,12,Fpreparing for the first moon mission
OL,13,Fsince 1972.
OL,15,FAfter years of work and $93bn spent to
OL,16,Fdate, the Artemis II mission will
OL,17,Finvolve a 10-day voyage around the
OL,18,FMoon, with NASA hoping this could pave
OL,19,Fthe way for an eventual lunar base on
OL,20,Fits surface.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
