OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775052666
OL,3,CWhat to know as countdown begins for
OL,4,Cfirst human Moon mission in 53 years
OL,6,FNASA's countdown clocks started
OL,7,Fticking on Monday afternoon at
OL,8,FFlorida's Kennedy Space Center. The 32-
OL,9,Fstorey Space Launch System rocket is
OL,10,Fpoised to blast off on Wednesday
OL,11,Fevening with four astronauts.
OL,13,FA liquid hydrogen leak during the
OL,14,Fpractice launch led to a delay in the
OL,15,Foperation, but now everything seems to
OL,16,Fbe going NASA's way as the countdown
OL,17,Fto launch proceeds.
OL,19,FITV explains.
OL,21,FWhat is Artemis?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
