OL,3,CWhat to know as countdown begins for
OL,4,Cfirst human Moon mission in 53 years
OL,6,FSpace travel is not just about
OL,7,Fexploration, but is also highly
OL,8,Fcompetitive, viewed by some countries
OL,9,Fas a mark of power, wealth, and global
OL,10,Finfluence.
OL,12,FIt has been over 50 years since the
OL,13,Fhistoric Apollo program, during which
OL,14,Fthe United States became the first
OL,15,Fcountry to land astronauts on the Moon
OL,16,Fin the so-called Space Race against
OL,17,Fthe Soviet Union.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
