PN,31412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775052666
OL,3,CWhat to know as countdown begins for
OL,4,Cfirst human Moon mission in 53 years
OL,6,FWhen is launch day and could it be
OL,7,Fdelayed?
OL,9,FAfter being postponed once due to bad
OL,10,Fweather in February, and then again
OL,11,Fafter the liquid hydrogen leak, there
OL,12,Fare always potential issues when
OL,13,Fplanning a high-stake mission.
OL,15,FThe weather is an important factor in
OL,16,Fdetermining if the mission will be
OL,17,Fable to go ahead and lightning is a
OL,18,Fbig safety risk, due to the Artemis II
OL,19,Frocket containing vast amounts of
OL,20,Fpropellant.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
