OL,3,CWhat to know as countdown begins for
OL,4,Cfirst human Moon mission in 53 years
OL,6,FCurrently the the weather looks
OL,7,Fpromising, with forecasters putting
OL,8,Fthe odds of favorable conditions at
OL,9,F80%.
OL,11,FThe space agency's meteorologists will
OL,12,Fbe the ones to decide if the
OL,13,Fconditions meet the criteria closer to
OL,14,Fthe time.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/13
